{"tid":2406450,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"Wordpress Hosting大比拼","createTime":"2021-02-13T08:08:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-13T14:00:16.000Z","uid":85524,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"472504796e7ff90450cfd2a1693387509cf576c3","tid":2406450,"uid":85524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T08:08:23.000Z","msg":"1. Bluehost<br />\n網上最多人推介，小弟中過伏。真心曲你個街，忍唔住爆粗。<br />\nBluehost個dashboard backend慢到著火 ，support判去印度，垃圾到食屎。<br />\n仲要佢個staging site plugin 伏到呢(未用過可以自己試下)<br />\n<br />\n2. Hostgator<br />\n未用過，但聽講同Bluehost 同一間公司。<br />\n<br />\n之後我都費是再搵shared hosting, 用GCP/Amazon算。<br />\n<br />\n大家有咩好野，分享下，幫下同行。"},{"pid":"ef892ffe059a24a149b9311dc4d38678beb8dde7","tid":2406450,"uid":46200,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T10:05:55.000Z","msg":"Wordpress hosting 未即係VPS<br />\n就算佢本身冇Wordpress 你都可以裝落去<br />\n<br />\nBtw<br />\n如果你乜都唔識，咁不如唔好自己host<br />\n如果你識少少，不如由頭自己整個網頁出嚟<br />\n<br />\nVPS嘅話，最平個plan 一般都夠用<br />\n依家比較hit嘅就vultr $3.5一個月，有ipv4<br />\n千其唔好貪平用vpsserver ，呢間嘢會無啦啦叫你自拍個人大頭同身分證，話係你身分有問題，然後封曬你啲credit 。我唔知佢collect 呢啲data做乜。呢間就$2.99一個月，唔怕死可以去。<br />\n<br />\n全部都係美金計算"},{"pid":"60c882bd3299fb6ec6b11f4d81858b941ac78244","tid":2406450,"uid":36465,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T10:12:25.000Z","msg":"無研究開呢啲細hosting<br />\n差得唔多既 自己直接用aws lightsail啦<br />\n都係幾蚊usd一個月<br />\n自己直接用aws唔驚比人搵笨<br />\n而lightsail界面都好易用 仲可以一開始揀幫你埋裝wordpress"},{"pid":"c792505a0bdf74f088838903b11eff53f1d6d2c3","tid":2406450,"uid":41134,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T10:12:41.000Z","msg":"aws lightsail<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2200fc5b6b5439b31ce160590eff349362f6c06","tid":2406450,"uid":106852,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T14:00:16.000Z","msg":"我純粹用黎寫blog，無太多要求，又費事花太多時間打理server，<a href=\"http://所以買wordpress.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E6%89%80%E4%BB%A5%E8%B2%B7wordpress.com&d=kdQtjCisvz5VKkzPdH2zQ%2FQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=000570cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">所以買wordpress.com</a>個人版就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}